{"surahDetails":{"id":102,"arabicName":"التكاثر","banglaName":"প্রাচুর্যের প্রতিযোগিতা","englishName":"Competition","enTranslatedName":"At-Takathur","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":28,"totalLetters":122,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/102.mp3","totalAyah":8},"surah":{"id":102,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","bangl_text":"প্রাচুর্যের লালসা তোমাদেরকে গাফেল রাখে","english_text":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6169.mp3","colorText":"أَلْهَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>كُمُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>تَّكَاثُرُ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","bangl_text":"এমনকি, তোমরা কবরস্থানে পৌছে যাও।","english_text":"Until you visit the graveyards","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6170.mp3","colorText":"حَتَّىٰ زُرْتُمُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْمَقَابِرَ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","bangl_text":"এটা কখনও উচিত নয়। তোমরা সত্ত্বরই জেনে নেবে।","english_text":"No! You are going to know","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6171.mp3","colorText":"كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَم<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>نَ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর এটা কখনও উচিত নয়। তোমরা সত্ত্বরই জেনে নেবে।","english_text":"Then no! You are going to know","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6172.mp3","colorText":"ثُ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>َ كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَم<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>نَ <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡ